<br>
3- Most people have no clue how a warrior works. Most of them are under the impression we mitigate way more than every other classes, that we have more hp, etc... Most think that taunt works whenever we press it. More importantly, people have the false impression that we can move proximity-based-aggro mobs when they are unstunnable and sitting in the middle of the chanters AEing...<br>
<br>
