3 - Its semi balanced. We are needed on raids (try raiding with 0 warriors) but we stack poorly. We are welcome to groups in most case because of historical reasons and false perceptions than true power. We are totally group dependant, which was fine until other classes were superior to us or close enough in every aspects. Then again, pallies and sk used to have no group at all, so i guess we shouldnt complain.<br>
